race.comment: POINT AND SHOOT (9) set to peak fourth up over his preferred trip. On the quick backup after returning good closing splits from last on the turn when fifth in the G3 Silver Eagle at this track last Saturday. Doesn't get his desired fast tempo but should prove too strong for these on the limit. VICTORIA ROAD (1) Group One Irish miler gelded over the lengthy break. Drops many grades for this after running last in the G1 Cantala over the mile at Flemington in 2023. Fitted with the two searching trials and the blinkers go on. Will roll forward and give a ton of cheek. FORTUNE (10) gets a better set-up today on the limit after shouldering the 60.5kg when a plugging sixth over 1600m in the Coonamble Cup. Won over this track and trip first-up and gets his chance. KINTYRE (4) capable on his day and ready for the mile third-up. Can stalk the speed and proven at this level. SUPER HELPFUL (12) tough old gelding who can sneak into the minor money after his good third at Warwick Farm.
